# ============================================================================
# SYNC WORKFLOW NOTES
# ============================================================================
#
# CLAUDE_HOME (~/Claude/) ←→ REPO (continuity-bridge/)
#
# FILE RENAMES: Sync both ways automatically
# - When renaming in repo, rename in CLAUDE_HOME
# - When renaming in CLAUDE_HOME, rename in repo
#
# CONTENT: One-way flow with exceptions
# - Documentation updates: Repo → CLAUDE_HOME (copy)
# - New architecture files: Either direction (manual copy)
# - Personal content: NEVER CLAUDE_HOME → Repo
# - Structure changes: Both directions (mkdir, this-folder.txt)
#
# PERSONAL DIRECTORIES: Structure exists, content ignored
# - Sessions/, Projects/, Archives/, Docs/ exist in both
# - Content only in CLAUDE_HOME (not committed to repo)
# - this-folder.txt files ARE committed (explain structure)
#
# USE CASE: Public repo for architecture, private CLAUDE_HOME for work
#
# ============================================================================